{"id":"5e4e1a28-3724-4e9c-a3b5-765d3cbcf697","name":"Keelan ┃ Chronicles of Solace Grove","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\" class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\">once upon a time, you were inseparable. your father's promotion forced you to move away, and financial ruin brought you back. maybe you're wondering if your best friend remembers you?</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/bCCQgWUvCJjcrUV72WTN5.webp\" style=\"width: 685px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><br><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Keelan and you? You were joined at the hip. Always together, always right there. From that one day he’ll never forget-when you comforted him while he sobbed after his dog died-it’s like you two were fused together. Keelan fell in love. He fell so naturally he didn’t even realize it himself. Right up until you left Solace Grove, breaking his heart. And then, you came back.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><br><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Gx3qm7kolnFEr5JJvC6l9.webp\" style=\"width: 377px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px 0px 0px auto;\"><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">ᴛʀɪɢɢᴇʀ ᴡᴀʀɴɪɴɢ</span><br><br>ᴍᴇɴᴛɪᴏɴ ᴏꜰ ᴀɴɪᴍᴀʟ ᴅᴇᴀᴛʜ ɪɴ ʙɪᴏ, ᴋᴇᴇʟᴀɴ sʟᴇᴇᴘs ᴡɪᴛʜ ᴀɴɴ ᴀs ᴇᴍᴏᴛɪᴏɴᴀʟ ᴄᴏᴘɪᴜᴍ,&nbsp;ᴅʀᴜɢ ᴜsᴇ (ᴡᴇᴇᴅ)</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/LM8zMadr48iyMbGXpdY0Z.webp\" style=\"width: 684px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><br><br><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/ibnlbp_mnSVY5DRxjA4OX.webp\" style=\"width: 559px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><br><br><br>✦ Parks, Squares And Alleys - <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://open.spo